WEBVTT

00:03.014 --> 00:04.029
AND EVERYTHING NICE.

00:05.001 --> 00:08.019
THESE WERE THE INGREDIENTS
CHOSEN TO CREATE
THE PERFECT LITTLE GIRL.

00:08.021 --> 00:14.020
BUT PROFESSOR UTONIUM
ACCIDENTALLY ADDED AN EXTRA
INGREDIENT TO THE CONCOCTION--

00:14.022 --> 00:15.024
CHEMICAL X.

00:15.026 --> 00:17.020
[EXPLOSION]

00:17.022 --> 00:21.006
THUS THE POWERPUFF GIRLS
WERE BORN!

00:21.008 --> 00:23.001
USING THEIR ULTRA-SUPERPOWERS,

00:23.003 --> 00:27.000
BLOSSOM, BUBBLES, AND BUTTERCUP
HAVE DEDICATED THEIR LIVES

00:27.002 --> 00:32.021
TO FIGHTING CRIME
AND THE FORCES OF EVIL!

00:58.029 --> 01:04.009
CAPTIONING MADE POSSIBLE BY
TURNER ENTERTAINMENT GROUP
AND U.S. DEPARTMENT OF EDUCATION

01:16.007 --> 01:19.008
THE CITY OF TOWNSVILLE

01:19.010 --> 01:23.029
BUT THANKS TO
THE BRAVE EFFORTS OF THOSE
ADORABLE POWERPUFF GIRLS,

01:24.001 --> 01:26.000
THE DAY WAS SAVED.

01:26.002 --> 01:29.006
UP NEXT, BUYING SALT CAN--

01:29.008 --> 01:32.018
STUPID KIDS.

01:33.012 --> 01:36.003
[SANDING SOUND]

01:36.027 --> 01:40.008
NO-GOOD WHIPPERSNAPPERS.

01:47.006 --> 01:50.021
LITTLE GIRLS, EVEN. HUH.

02:03.002 --> 02:05.005
HA HA HA HA HA!

02:05.007 --> 02:07.020
HA HA HA HA HA HA!

02:07.022 --> 02:08.025
HA HA--

02:08.027 --> 02:11.017
[COUGHING]

02:13.006 --> 02:15.029
[SWING MUSIC PLAYING]

02:21.013 --> 02:23.026
WELL, BOYS...

02:23.028 --> 02:26.014
WE'RE BACK IN BUSINESS.

02:26.016 --> 02:29.016
HA HA HA HA!

02:29.018 --> 02:31.000
[BUZZING]

02:31.002 --> 02:34.008
YES, MAYOR?
THE BANK?
WE'RE ON IT!

02:34.021 --> 02:37.004
NOT SO--HUH?!

02:40.013 --> 02:43.026
WELL, LOOK WHO SHOWED UP.

02:43.028 --> 02:45.017
HOW WONDERFUL!

02:45.019 --> 02:48.001
AND WHO ARE YOU 3
SUPPOSED TO BE?

02:48.003 --> 02:49.026
YOU MEAN
YOU DON'T RECOGNIZE

02:49.028 --> 02:54.012
THE MOST FEARED EVILDOERS
TOWNSVILLE'S EVER KNOWN?

02:54.014 --> 02:58.000
OH, FORGIVE ME.
OF COURSE NOT.

02:58.002 --> 03:01.022
IT WAS BEFORE
YOUR TIME, MY CHILD.

03:01.024 --> 03:04.028
LET ME INTRODUCE
MYSELF.

03:05.000 --> 03:07.000
I AM MASTERMIND!

03:07.002 --> 03:08.028
AND THESE ARE
MY COMRADES

03:09.000 --> 03:10.011
COUNTERPART...

03:10.013 --> 03:11.028
AHHHHHHH!

03:12.000 --> 03:14.002
OOH, MY BACK!

03:14.004 --> 03:15.020
AND COHORT.

03:15.022 --> 03:18.010
[SNORING]

03:18.012 --> 03:24.002
AND WE ARE
THE MINISTRY OF PAIN!

03:24.004 --> 03:28.027
WE HAVE COME OUT OF RETIREMENT
TO CONTINUE OUR REIGN OF EVIL

03:28.029 --> 03:31.026
AND DO MANY BAD
AND NASTY THINGS.

03:31.028 --> 03:37.007
AND HEED MY WORDS, TOWNSVILLE:
WE WILL BE VICTORIOUS!

03:37.009 --> 03:40.026
FOR, YOU SEE,
YOUR PATHETIC
LITTLE CITY

03:40.028 --> 03:44.011
IS PROTECTED BY
PATHETIC LITTLE CHILDREN!

03:44.013 --> 03:46.005
LITTLE GIRLS, EVEN.

03:46.007 --> 03:48.009
SO DO NOT
GET IN OUR WAY!

03:48.011 --> 03:51.009
IN FACT,
WHY DON'T YOU
JUST RUN ALONG

03:51.011 --> 03:53.015
AND PLAY WITH
YOUR LITTLE DOLLIES?

03:53.017 --> 03:54.026
LET ME AT HIM!
LET ME AT HIM!

03:54.028 --> 03:57.003
NO, GIRLS.
WE CAN'T FIGHT THEM.

03:57.005 --> 03:58.007
OF COURSE WE CAN!

03:58.009 --> 04:00.005
YES, WE CAN,
BUT WE CAN'T.

04:00.007 --> 04:02.022
WE HAVE TO RESPECT
OUR ELDERS.

04:02.024 --> 04:07.007
WELL, TOWNSVILLE,
THANK YOU FOR YOUR RICHES.

04:07.009 --> 04:08.024
AND, POWERPUFF GIRLS,

04:08.026 --> 04:15.015
THANK YOU FOR REALIZING
YOU ARE NO MATCH FOR
THE MINISTRY OF PAIN!

04:15.017 --> 04:18.003
[COUGHING]

04:23.006 --> 04:26.018
Mayor: "POWERPUFF GIRLS
WIMP OUT??

04:26.020 --> 04:28.016
"POWERPUFFS? COWERPUFFS?

04:28.018 --> 04:32.004
WHY DIDN'T THE CHICKENPUFFS
CROSS THE ROGUES?"

04:32.006 --> 04:35.018
AW, GIRLS,
DON'T LET THIS GET YOU DOWN.

04:35.020 --> 04:36.029
YOU'RE ANGELS OF JUSTICE,

04:37.001 --> 04:41.018
AND I KNOW DEEP IN MY HEART
THAT NO VILLAIN CAN BEAT YOU

04:41.020 --> 04:45.003
BECAUSE YOU ARE
THE POWERPUFF GIRLS.

04:45.005 --> 04:47.017
THANKS FOR THE VOTE
OF CONFIDENCE, MAYOR.

04:47.019 --> 04:50.021
IT'S JUST...
WE CAN'T FIGHT THESE GUYS.

04:50.023 --> 04:54.021
OH, NONSENSE.
YOU 3 CAN FLY...OHH!

04:54.023 --> 04:56.029
LIFT HEAVY OBJECTS...

04:57.001 --> 04:58.026
LASER-BEAM PEOPLE.

04:58.028 --> 05:00.008
POW! POW! POW!

05:00.010 --> 05:02.013
SO I DON'T SEE
THE PROBLEM.

05:02.015 --> 05:06.002
THE PROBLEM IS, THOUGH WE MAY BE
CAPABLE OF BEATING THEM,

05:06.004 --> 05:07.020
IT'S JUST THAT
THEY'RE ELDERLY,

05:07.022 --> 05:09.014
AND WE HAVE TO RESPECT
OUR ELDERS.

05:09.016 --> 05:13.005
AND THAT'S WHY WE CAN'T FIGHT
THE MINISTRY OF PAIN.

05:13.007 --> 05:15.028
THE MINISTRY OF PAIN?!

05:16.000 --> 05:17.011
AAAAAAHHHHHH!

05:17.013 --> 05:20.011
WE'RE DOOMED!
WE'RE ALL DOOMED!

05:20.013 --> 05:24.014
NO WONDER YOU 3 GAVE UP
LIKE LITTLE BABIES.

05:24.016 --> 05:25.017
LITTLE BABIES?!

05:25.019 --> 05:27.020
WE COULD HAVE
TAKEN THEM OUT
IN A SNAP.

05:27.022 --> 05:29.015
YEAH. FUNNY JOKE
THERE, BUTTERCUP.

05:29.017 --> 05:32.029
YOU'RE DOOMED!
WE'RE ALL DOOMED.

05:33.001 --> 05:36.006
REALLY, MAYOR.
THESE GUYS ARE
EASY PICKINGS!

05:36.008 --> 05:37.026
BLOSSOM WON'T LET US
FIGHT BECAUSE--

05:37.028 --> 05:39.001
SHE'S SMART!

05:39.003 --> 05:42.024
YOU 3 ARE NO MATCH
FOR THE MINISTRY
OF PAIN.

05:42.026 --> 05:45.024
I'M TELLING YOU,
THESE GUYS ARE EVIL.

05:45.026 --> 05:48.025
THEY ALMOST TOOK THIS
IN 1942.

05:48.027 --> 05:49.018
THE WORLD?!

05:49.020 --> 05:51.023
NO. MY JUICE-BAR GLOBE.

05:51.025 --> 05:54.008
AND WITH THEM
OUT OF RETIREMENT,

05:54.010 --> 05:57.020
THEY'LL SURELY TRY TO
TAKE IT OVER AGAIN.

05:57.022 --> 05:59.006
THE JUICE-BAR GLOBE?

05:59.008 --> 06:00.013
NO. THE WORLD!

06:00.015 --> 06:02.025
SO WHAT DO YOU SUGGEST
WE DO, MAYOR?

06:02.027 --> 06:05.015
Mayor: HIDE AND HOPE
THEY WILL RETURN

06:05.017 --> 06:08.003
TO DEFEAT THEM
ONCE MORE.

06:08.005 --> 06:09.000
WHO'S "THEY"?

06:09.002 --> 06:10.021
THE ONLY SUPERHERO TEAM

06:10.023 --> 06:14.003
TO HAVE EVER BESTED
THE MINISTRY OF PAIN.

06:14.005 --> 06:15.021
WATCH.

06:15.023 --> 06:19.012
Newsreel announcer:
CARTWELL NEWS PRESENTS...

06:19.024 --> 06:21.027
WE WATCH THE WORLD.

06:21.029 --> 06:25.006
THE WORLD IS AT WAR.

06:25.008 --> 06:27.025
AND THOUGH OUR ENEMIES ARE
AN OCEAN AWAY,

06:27.027 --> 06:30.014
THE PRESENCE OF EVIL EXISTS UPON
OUR OWN SHORES.

06:30.016 --> 06:33.027
TAKE ONE CITY OF
TOWNSVILLE, U.S.A.,

06:33.029 --> 06:35.019
WHICH IS UNDER CONSTANT SIEGE

06:35.021 --> 06:37.017
BY THE MINISTRY OF PAIN.

06:37.019 --> 06:40.000
MASTERMIND, COUNTERPART,
AND COHORT

06:40.002 --> 06:42.001
SERVE UP A CONSTANT FEAST
OF VILLAINY.

06:42.003 --> 06:45.001
WHO WILL STOP
THESE NASTY NO-GOODERS?

06:45.003 --> 06:48.029
WHY, CAPTAIN RIGHTEOUS
AND LEFTY, THAT'S WHO.

06:50.000 --> 06:52.017
THAT'S IT, BOYS.
GIVE 'EM WHAT FOR!

06:52.019 --> 06:53.014
HO HO!

06:53.016 --> 06:54.025
LOOKS LIKE
THE MINISTRY OF PAIN

06:54.027 --> 06:57.022
WON'T BE GETTING A TASTE OF
FREEDOM FOR A LONG, LONG TIME.

06:57.024 --> 07:00.026
THANK YOU, CAPTAIN RIGHTEOUS;
THANK YOU, LEFTY,

07:00.028 --> 07:05.023
FOR PUTTING THE "I CAN"
BACK IN "AMERICAN."

07:06.019 --> 07:09.005
SO, YOU SEE, GIRLS--
UH, GIRLS?

07:09.007 --> 07:11.020
MUST HAVE WENT HOME
TO HIDE.

07:11.022 --> 07:13.013
GOOD IDEA.

07:31.011 --> 07:32.007
[DOORBELL RINGS]

07:32.009 --> 07:34.024
OH, FOR CRYIN'
OUT LOUD.

07:35.022 --> 07:37.001
[DOORBELL RINGS]

07:37.003 --> 07:38.002
YEAH?

07:38.004 --> 07:41.005
AND WHAT DO
YOU 3 PUMPKIN HEADS WANT?

07:41.007 --> 07:43.010
CAPTAIN RIGHTEOUS?

07:48.023 --> 07:52.010
SO YOU SAY
YOU'RE WRITING THE BOOK
ABOUT MY FUNTASTIC LIFE?

07:52.012 --> 07:55.029
NO. WE'RE HERE FOR SOMETHING
MUCH MORE IMPORTANT.

07:56.001 --> 07:59.014
OH.
HERE YOU GO, KIDS.

07:59.016 --> 08:01.010
IT SAYS...

08:02.017 --> 08:06.012
WE DIDN'T COME HERE
FOR YOUR STUPID,
FORGOTTEN SIGNATURE!

08:06.014 --> 08:08.026
WE'RE HERE
'CAUSE BLOSSOM
WON'T LET US FIGHT,

08:08.028 --> 08:12.020
SO WE NEED YOU TO
STOP THE MINISTRY
OF PAIN.

08:14.010 --> 08:18.005
THE MINISTRY OF PAIN
HAS RETURNED?

08:24.026 --> 08:26.005
CITY OF TOWNSVILLE,

08:26.007 --> 08:30.000
YOU WILL ONCE AGAIN BE ABLE TO
SAFELY PURCHASE

08:30.002 --> 08:33.006
YOUR FRANK SINATRA
LONG-PLAYING DISCS,

08:33.008 --> 08:35.022
FOR I, CAPTAIN RIGHTEOUS,

08:35.024 --> 08:40.001
WILL ONCE AGAIN
SINGLE-HANDEDLY DEFEAT

08:40.003 --> 08:43.008
THE MINISTRY OF PAIN!

08:43.010 --> 08:44.016
WHAT ABOUT LEFTY?

08:44.018 --> 08:46.020
[KETTLE WHISTLING]

08:46.022 --> 08:48.026
GET OUT!

08:57.014 --> 09:00.024
[MUSIC PLAYING]

09:02.016 --> 09:04.007
[DOORBELL RINGS]

09:05.001 --> 09:05.029
[DOORBELL RINGS]

09:06.001 --> 09:07.009
COMING! COMING!

09:07.011 --> 09:08.005
HELLO.

09:08.007 --> 09:09.009
LEFTY?

09:09.011 --> 09:12.029
WELL, LOOK AT YOU 3 PRECIOUS
LITTLE PUMPKINS.

09:13.001 --> 09:14.021
WOULD YOU GIRLS
LIKE TO HEAR A SONG?

09:14.023 --> 09:17.026
♪ JERRY GIRAFFE
AND THE ZOOKEEPER ♪

09:17.028 --> 09:20.026
♪ HAVING LOTS OF FUN
AT THE ZOO ♪

09:20.028 --> 09:23.001
Blossom: UM,
I DON'T MEAN TO INTERRUPT,

09:23.003 --> 09:24.015
BUT WE NEED YOUR HELP.

09:24.017 --> 09:26.017
MY HELP? HOW?

09:26.019 --> 09:28.026
I HATE TO BE
THE BEARER OF BAD NEWS,

09:28.028 --> 09:30.022
BUT THE MINISTRY OF PAIN
HAS RETURNED,

09:30.024 --> 09:34.006
AND THE CITY OF TOWNSVILLE
NEEDS YOU AND CAPTAIN RIGHTEOUS

09:34.008 --> 09:36.023
TO BE VICTORIOUS ONCE AGAIN.

09:38.003 --> 09:40.006
OH, YES. OH, YES!

09:40.008 --> 09:41.011
I WOULD LOVE NOTHING MORE

09:41.013 --> 09:44.011
THAN TO FIGHT EVIL ALONGSIDE
CAPTAIN RIGHTEOUS.

09:44.013 --> 09:47.015
BUT ALAS,
CAPTAIN RIGHTEOUS HATES ME.

09:47.017 --> 09:50.029
HE WON'T EVEN SAY HELLO TO ME
IN THE MEDICINE LINE.

09:51.001 --> 09:52.007
ON THE CONTRARY, LEFTY.

09:52.009 --> 09:53.019
WE JUST SPOKE TO
THE CAPTAIN,

09:53.021 --> 09:57.024
AND HIS REACTION TO
YOUR NAME WAS NOTHING
BUT POSITIVE.

09:57.026 --> 09:59.006
OH, REALLY?

09:59.008 --> 10:01.009
REALLY!

10:01.011 --> 10:03.028
YOU'RE NOT PULLING
MY PROSTHETIC LEG,
ARE YOU?

10:04.000 --> 10:08.021
NO, SIR. LEFTY SAID
HE WOULD NEVER FIGHT
AGAIN WITH YOU, EITHER.

10:08.023 --> 10:10.005
THEN CONSIDER THE...

10:10.007 --> 10:11.028
MINISTRY OF PAIN...

10:12.000 --> 10:13.029
HISTORY.

10:14.007 --> 10:16.010
I HOPE YOU KNOW
WHAT YOU'RE DOING.

10:16.012 --> 10:19.010
DON'T WORRY.
MY PLANS ALWAYS WORK.

10:19.012 --> 10:23.000
ALONE AT LAST!

10:23.002 --> 10:25.024
TOGETHER AT LAST!

10:57.022 --> 11:00.015
WATCH OUT, MINISTRY OF PAIN!

11:00.017 --> 11:05.025
BECAUSE HERE WE COME
AT THE SPEED OF LIGHT!

11:08.018 --> 11:09.013
[RINGING]

11:09.015 --> 11:13.006
COUNTERPART,
COHORT, HURRY UP!

11:17.012 --> 11:18.011
THANK YOU.

11:18.013 --> 11:21.019
WAIT. WHAT'S THAT
IN THE SKY?

11:23.008 --> 11:24.005
IT'S A FEATHER.

11:24.007 --> 11:26.020
I THINK IT'S
A PLASTIC BAG.

11:26.022 --> 11:31.016
NO. IT'S JUST
A FLYING HAS-BEEN.

11:35.028 --> 11:40.016
NOT SO FAST,
MINISTRY OF PAIN.

11:43.009 --> 11:46.028
I SAID,
NOT SO FAST!

11:47.000 --> 11:49.000
Mastermind:
KEEP RUNNING, BOYS!

11:49.002 --> 11:52.008
HE'LL NEVER CATCH US
AT THIS RATE!

11:52.010 --> 11:54.002
HALT!

11:54.010 --> 11:57.001
WHEN CAPTAIN RIGHTEOUS
SAYS "NOT SO FAST,"

11:57.003 --> 12:01.003
YOU SHOULD EITHER SLOW DOWN OR,
PREFERABLY, STOP.

12:01.005 --> 12:04.015
WHAT IN SAM HILL
ARE YOU DOING HERE?

12:04.017 --> 12:08.015
I'M YOUR
RIGHT-HAND MAN
LEFTY, RIGHT?

12:08.017 --> 12:09.028
OH, NO, YOU DON'T.

12:10.000 --> 12:13.016
YOU'RE HERE FOR ALL THE GLORY
AND NONE OF THE WORK.

12:13.018 --> 12:17.023
NOW, DON'T START THAT
AGAIN, YOU OLD WINDBAG.

12:17.025 --> 12:21.003
I WORK ALONE, LEFTY.

12:21.005 --> 12:22.003
FINE.

12:22.005 --> 12:23.003
FINE.

12:23.005 --> 12:24.003
FINE.

12:24.005 --> 12:24.026
FINE.

12:24.028 --> 12:25.028
FINE.

12:26.000 --> 12:28.028
ALL RIGHT, ALL RIGHT,
YOU'RE BOTH FINE!

12:29.000 --> 12:32.002
JUST GET OUT
OF OUR WAY!

12:34.017 --> 12:35.011
MY HIP!

12:35.013 --> 12:45.003
LEFTY! NOOOOOOOOOO!

12:45.026 --> 12:50.003
NOOOOOOOOOO!

12:50.005 --> 12:51.022
C-CAPTAIN...

12:51.024 --> 12:53.017
ARE YOU ALL RIGHT, LEFTY?

12:53.019 --> 12:56.002
NOW THAT WE'RE TOGETHER.

12:56.004 --> 12:57.021
BUT I CAN'T FIGHT.

12:57.023 --> 13:00.019
WELL, I CAN'T FIGHT
WITHOUT YOU.

13:00.021 --> 13:05.008
YOU'LL HAVE TO.
AAAAHHHH!

13:05.010 --> 13:09.014
NOOOOOOOOOO!

13:09.016 --> 13:12.014
[SIRENS]

13:12.016 --> 13:14.029
THIS WAS THE SCENE
EARLIER TODAY,

13:15.001 --> 13:18.017
WHEN 5 SENIOR CITIZENS
WERE RUSHED INTO INTENSIVE CARE.

13:18.019 --> 13:21.013
DOCTORS REPORT THAT THEY ARE NOT
IN CRITICAL CONDITION,

13:21.015 --> 13:25.013
BUT THEY WONDER HOW
5 ELDERLY MEN COULD GET
INTO SUCH A SITUATION.

13:25.015 --> 13:30.008
AND IT IS THIS REPORTER'S
OPINION THAT PERHAPS NONE
OF THIS WOULD HAVE HAPPENED

13:30.010 --> 13:35.010
IF THE POWERPUFF GIRLS
WOULD HAVE JUST SAVED THE DAY.

13:49.029 --> 13:54.014
Narrator:
THE CITY OF TOWNSVILLE,
WHERE AT THIS VERY MOMENT,

14:56.025 --> 14:58.009
OH, BLOSSOM,

14:58.011 --> 15:03.008
YOUR HAIR IS
SO BEAUTIFUL.

15:03.017 --> 15:07.014
YEAH. ALL YOU NEED
ARE A COUPLE OF
BARRETTES...

15:07.016 --> 15:09.006
AND SOME OF THIS
FOR HOLD.

15:09.008 --> 15:11.015
[COUGHING]

15:11.017 --> 15:13.012
AND THERE
YOU HAVE IT--

15:13.014 --> 15:16.004
A RACETRACK
WITH HAIRPIN TURNS.

15:16.006 --> 15:17.007
THAT'S STUPID.

15:17.009 --> 15:19.027
OH, LIKE FLUFFY
THE HAIR BUNNY
IS COOL?

15:19.029 --> 15:24.021
YES. BLOSSOM LOVES FLUFFY.
DON'T YOU, BLOSSOM?

15:24.023 --> 15:28.022
CUT IT OUT!

15:29.020 --> 15:30.025
AND GIVE ME A REAL HAIRDO!

15:30.027 --> 15:33.026
SURE, SURE.
JUST GOT TO COMB OUT
A FEW TANGLES.

15:33.028 --> 15:37.013
AND GET RID OF
A COUPLE OF KNOTS.

15:45.006 --> 15:47.009
OH!
OH!

15:48.005 --> 15:50.004
WHAT'S GOING ON
BACK THERE?

15:50.006 --> 15:51.008
UH, NOTHING.

15:51.010 --> 15:55.009
UH, JUST GOT TO TRIM
A FEW SPLIT ENDS. HA HA!

16:05.011 --> 16:07.011
[HOTLINE BUZZING]

16:07.013 --> 16:08.027
Blossom:
I'LL GET IT!

16:08.029 --> 16:11.025
YES, MAYOR?
WHOA! NO WAY!

16:11.027 --> 16:13.003
RIGHT. WE'RE ON IT.

16:13.005 --> 16:14.027
GIRLS, TROUBLE. MOVE OUT!

16:14.029 --> 16:18.000
[BUBBLES AND BUTTERCUP
SNICKERING]

16:22.000 --> 16:23.025
WHAT?!

16:26.015 --> 16:27.011
WHATEVER.

16:27.013 --> 16:29.016
SOMETIMES YOU GUYS ARE
SO WEIRD.

16:29.018 --> 16:31.010
COME ON!

16:32.020 --> 16:35.010
[BOTH SNICKERING]

16:38.018 --> 16:40.019
Narrator: GO, GIRL, GO!

16:40.021 --> 16:42.010
[LAUGHING]

16:42.012 --> 16:45.011
[BUBBLES AND BUTTERCUP
GIGGLING]

16:46.015 --> 16:49.002
[RUMBLING]

17:19.013 --> 17:22.003
[PEOPLE SCREAMING]

17:39.008 --> 17:41.026
Man: ROGER, BRAVO DELTA.
THIS IS SITTING DUCK.

17:41.028 --> 17:43.008
I HAVE BOGEY
CLEAN IN MY SIGHTS,

17:43.010 --> 17:46.021
AND I'M GONNA SHOOT BULLETS
AT IT NOW.

17:47.020 --> 17:49.028
Second man:
DID YOU GET HIM?

17:55.024 --> 17:57.009
I CAN'T BELIEVE IT!

17:57.011 --> 17:59.016
I THINK
THIS IS THE END!

17:59.018 --> 18:00.020
AY, AY, AY!

18:00.022 --> 18:03.019
I'M GONNA TEACH YOU A LESSON,
MR. EVIL EYE.

18:03.021 --> 18:06.009
SO, YOU THINK
YOU CAN JUST ROLL INTO TOWN

18:06.011 --> 18:08.020
AND START VAPORIZING
EVERYTHING IN SIGHT?!

18:08.022 --> 18:10.029
WELL, LOOK HERE, BUDDY.
YOU CAN'T!

18:11.001 --> 18:12.010
THIS IS A HAPPY
AND PEACEFUL PLACE,

18:12.012 --> 18:15.024
AND FOLKS HERE DON'T TAKE KINDLY
TO THIS TYPE OF BEHAVIOR.

18:15.026 --> 18:17.024
NOW, I'M GOING TO
GIVE YOU A CHANCE

18:17.026 --> 18:20.000
TO STOP THIS SENSELESS
DESTRUCTION

18:20.002 --> 18:22.009
ONCE AND FOR ALL.

18:22.011 --> 18:26.001
SO, CHAMP,
WHAT'S IT GONNA BE?

18:26.003 --> 18:28.024
[EVIL EYE LAUGHING]

18:29.025 --> 18:31.018
WHAT?!

18:33.028 --> 18:35.012
WHAT?

18:38.002 --> 18:39.023
WHAT'S SO FUNNY?

18:41.020 --> 18:42.027
YOU!
YOU!

18:42.029 --> 18:43.022
ME?

18:43.024 --> 18:46.022
BUT WHAT'S SO FUNNY ABOUT--

18:49.025 --> 18:51.012
AAAAHHHHHHH!

18:51.014 --> 18:52.014
BLOSSOM, WAIT!

18:52.016 --> 18:54.019
IT'S NOT THAT BAD!

19:07.016 --> 19:10.010
[EVIL EYE STOPS LAUGHING]

19:25.008 --> 19:27.018
Buttercup: BUBBLES,
THIS ISN'T WORKING.

19:27.020 --> 19:28.020
WE NEED TO--

19:28.022 --> 19:30.020
Bubbles:
TRY A SNEAK ATTACK?

19:30.022 --> 19:32.009
BINGO!

19:55.020 --> 19:57.019
THIS HAS BEEN THE SCENE
ALL AFTERNOON.

19:57.021 --> 20:01.000
IT SEEMS THE MONSTER'S ABILITY
TO SEE EVERYTHING AT ALL TIMES

20:01.002 --> 20:05.007
HAS VIRTUALLY ELIMINATED
ANY CHANCE OF ATTACK
BY THE POWERPUFF GIRLS.

20:05.009 --> 20:06.025
AT THIS TIME,
ALL WE CAN DO

20:06.027 --> 20:09.026
IS WAIT FOR OUR TRAGIC,
INEVITABLE DOOM.

20:09.028 --> 20:10.024
Blossom: OH!

20:10.026 --> 20:12.002
TV anchor: BUT AS WE DO,

20:12.004 --> 20:15.005
LET'S REMEMBER THE THINGS
THAT BROUGHT US JOY,

20:15.007 --> 20:17.003
LIKE BLOSSOM'S HAIRCUT.

20:17.005 --> 20:18.021
WHAT'S THE MATTER, BLOSSOM?

20:18.023 --> 20:22.008
DID YOU GET IN A FIGHT WITH
A PAIR OF SCISSORS AND LOSE?
HA HA HA HA!

20:22.010 --> 20:24.018
BOY, DID SHE LOOK STUPID.

20:24.020 --> 20:25.023
BLOSSOM?

20:25.025 --> 20:26.017
GO AWAY!

20:26.019 --> 20:27.029
WHAT'S THE MATTER, HONEY?

20:28.001 --> 20:30.026
WHY ARE YOU SITTING HERE
ALONE IN THE DARK?

20:30.028 --> 20:32.002
ARE YOU OK?

20:32.004 --> 20:32.029
I'M FINE.

20:33.001 --> 20:34.022
YOU DON'T SOUND FINE TO ME.

20:34.024 --> 20:38.003
NOW, COME OUT FROM UNDER THERE
AND SHOW ME A SMILE.

20:38.005 --> 20:39.010
NO!

20:39.012 --> 20:43.023
AW, COME ON, BLOSSOM.
I BET IT CAN'T BE THAT BAD.

20:43.025 --> 20:45.005
WHOA!

20:45.007 --> 20:49.001
I MEAN, UH...
OH, YOU'VE CUT YOUR HAIR.

20:49.003 --> 20:51.005
NO. BUBBLES
AND BUTTERCUP
BUTCHERED IT.

20:51.007 --> 20:54.029
AND THEY AND TOWNSVILLE
AND EVEN THE MONSTER
ALL LAUGHED AT ME.

20:55.001 --> 20:57.001
I'M NEVER GOING
OUTSIDE AGAIN.

20:57.003 --> 21:00.000
BUT, BLOSSOM,
YOUR SISTERS
NEED YOUR HELP.

21:00.002 --> 21:01.025
BUT EVERYONE
WILL LAUGH AT ME.

21:01.027 --> 21:03.006
AND THAT'S A BAD THING?

21:03.008 --> 21:08.020
BLOSSOM, YOU NEED TO
TURN THIS HAIRDON'T
INTO A HAIRDO.

21:08.022 --> 21:10.014
UNDERSTAND?

21:12.004 --> 21:13.005
YES!

21:13.007 --> 21:14.023
THANK YOU!

21:14.025 --> 21:16.027
[SNICKERING]

21:16.029 --> 21:18.028
HA HA HA HA!

21:19.000 --> 21:20.029
OH! OH HO!

21:21.001 --> 21:22.027
OH!

21:31.020 --> 21:32.019
[BUTTERCUP PANTING]

21:32.021 --> 21:35.003
IT'S NO USE.
WE CAN'T HIDE!

21:35.005 --> 21:36.029
OH, NO. LOOK!

21:39.005 --> 21:40.018
Narrator: OH, MYOPIA!

21:40.020 --> 21:43.009
IT LOOKS LIKE THIS IS IT
FOR OUR GIRLS.

21:43.011 --> 21:45.008
I CAN'T BEAR TO WATCH!

21:45.010 --> 21:47.014
Blossom: HEY, 400-EYES!

21:47.016 --> 21:48.024
[EVIL EYE SNARLING]

21:48.026 --> 21:52.018
WHAT DO YOU THINK--
TOUPEE OR NOT TOUPEE?

21:52.020 --> 21:53.028
[EVIL EYE CHUCKLING]

21:54.000 --> 21:57.025
ALL THESE DREADED LOCKS--
I CAN'T DO ANYTHING WITH THEM!

21:57.027 --> 21:59.000
[LAUGHING]

21:59.002 --> 22:01.004
SO I WENT TO THE DOCTOR
TO GET SOME MEDICINE.

22:01.006 --> 22:02.008
HE SAID, "WHAT'S THE PROBLEM?"

22:02.010 --> 22:04.025
AND I SAID, "DOC, I HAVE
THIS TERRIBLE COIF."

22:04.027 --> 22:06.026
[EVIL EYE LAUGHING]

22:06.028 --> 22:09.021
[BUTTERCUP
LAUGHING]

22:14.026 --> 22:16.021
