Buttercup, look.

22:16.023 --> 22:20.028
[EVIL EYE LAUGHING]

22:28.007 --> 22:30.018
[CROWD LAUGHING]

22:31.024 --> 22:35.025
OK, OK, I KNOW.
MY HAIR LOOKS STUPID.

22:35.027 --> 22:37.002
NO, BLOSSOM.

22:37.004 --> 22:39.019
WE'RE LAUGHING
'CAUSE WE'RE HAPPY.

22:39.021 --> 22:40.020
HA HA! YEAH!

22:40.022 --> 22:43.002
WE THOUGHT
WE WERE GONERS!

22:43.004 --> 22:46.013
BUT WE'RE ALL REALLY SORRY
WE LAUGHED AT YOU.

22:46.015 --> 22:47.018
YEAH.

22:47.020 --> 22:48.017
REALLY?

22:48.019 --> 22:51.002
HA HA HA HA HA!

22:51.004 --> 22:54.012
BUT STILL,
I DO LOOK REALLY STUPID.

22:54.014 --> 22:58.002
I'LL SAY!
HA HA HA HA HA!

22:58.004 --> 22:59.006
STUPID.

22:59.008 --> 23:02.015
HA HA HA HA!
SO, WE'RE EVEN?

23:03.019 --> 23:05.001
Blossom: YEAH, WE'RE EVEN.

